txt.en: 'Meow! Hello, I'm Tens! Although I type slowly, due to my furry paws, I can help you complete the Epic quest series. If you complete this quest, you'll be flagged as having completed Book I of the Epic series.
'Alright, when you complete this quest you'll be flagged as having completed Book I of the Epic. Have fun!'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book I of the Epic quest series.
